# Nicholas Cross (2129-2215), professor
# Clayton Cross (2140-2214), museum worker

From 2152 to 2164, Cross dated an insurance agent named Helen Davis (2114-2197). They had a son:

# Buster Cross (2154-after 2217), flight attendant

From 2164 to 2188, Cross dated a Moroccan-British firewoman named Manal Omarat (2146-after 2204). They had three children:

# August Cross (2165-after 2217), translator
# Renesmee Cross III (2177-after 2217), firewoman
# Keith Cross (2178-after 2217), librarian

In 2188, Cross started dating an Uruguayan-British unemployed woman named Florencia Martinez (2170-after 2217). They had five children:

# Dixie Cross (2190-after 2217)
# Tiara Cross (2192-after 2217), policewoman
